#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:2
#: ff67b8489fd548d0acd931976d071f8c
msgid "外设"
msgstr "Peripherals"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:17
#: 6b99a58d4a6547b8befece4f994e1e6b
msgid "ADC的精度和采样率是多少？"
msgstr "What are the ADC resolution and sampling rate?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:18
#: 9f518909171542f8baeab43cb515413f
msgid ""
"ADC实际精度为12BIT,当OSR=256,打开平均值滤波的时候可以达到16bit精度。 当ADC工"
"作在非多通道扫描模式时,最大可支持2M采样率。 如果是多通道扫描模式，最大支持1M"
"采样率。"
msgstr ""
"The actual ADC resolution is 12-bit. When OSR=256 and average filtering is "
"enabled, it can reach 16-bit resolution. When the ADC works in non-multi-"
"channel scan mode, the maximum supported sampling rate is 2M. In multi-"
"channel scan mode, the maximum supported sampling rate is 1M."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:23
#: 1cae6b750e3547f2b1bef61a54306a63
msgid "mtimer的作用是什么，它是如何工作的？"
msgstr "What is the function of mtimer and how does it work?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:24
#: f05f52b9d36a4cba98a129af946cb893
msgid ""
"MTimer为内核提供的一个timer，开启后实现计时功能，计数值与比较值寄存器位于内"
"核，使用方式与一般timer无明显区别。"
msgstr ""
"MTimer is a timer provided by the core. After it is enabled, it provides "
"timing functionality. The counter value and compare value registers are "
"located in the core. Its usage is not significantly different from a normal "
"timer."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:27
#: 8e36d6d2ca474ce6acc7552a71efd489
msgid "模组包含几个timer?"
msgstr "How many timers does the module contain?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:28
#: 6c3eaced2bec423f924de329dd8ca773
msgid "1个64-bit mtimer，2个32-bit normal timer，1个16-bit watchdog timer。"
msgstr ""
"It contains one 64-bit mtimer, two 32-bit normal timers, and one 16-bit "
"watchdog timer."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:32
#: d1b7571e83984057aebe703c097b45c0
msgid "看门狗的超时时间如何设置？超时的现象是什么？"
msgstr "How is the watchdog timeout set? What happens when it times out?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:33
#: 43503f7a16254c808e33687492e1f683
msgid ""
"看门狗包含一个计数器和比较器，通过写入比较器的值，当计数器向上计数达到比较器"
"的值时，会产生一个看门狗中断信号或者一个系统复位信号， 具体产生哪种信号由用户"
"自行设置。"
msgstr ""
"The watchdog includes a counter and a comparator. By writing a value to the "
"comparator, when the counter counts upward and reaches the comparator value, "
"a watchdog interrupt signal or a system reset signal will be generated. "
"Which signal is generated is configured by the user."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:38
#: 11593106dee54f288d2107fa9feacd23
msgid "GPIO的配置参数有哪些？如何配置？"
msgstr "What are the GPIO configuration parameters? How are they configured?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:39
#: f751429417774649a43fd7805f9b1348
msgid ""
"gpioPin : GPIO pin number， GPIO编号 gpioFun : GPIO function， GPIO功能 "
"gpioMode : input/output/af， 输入/输出/复用模式 pullType : pull_up/pull_down/"
"pull_none， 上拉/下拉/浮空 drive : drive strength， 驱动能力， 数值越大驱动能"
"力越强 smtCtrl : smt, 迟滞控制，建议设一 详情参见低RM GPIO章节。"
msgstr ""
"gpioPin: GPIO pin number. gpioFun: GPIO function. gpioMode: input/output/af, "
"input/output/alternate function mode. pullType: pull_up/pull_down/pull_none, "
"pull-up/pull-down/floating. drive: drive strength; the larger the value, the "
"stronger the drive capability. smtCtrl: smt, hysteresis control, recommended "
"to be set to 1. For details, refer to the GPIO section of the RM."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:45
#: 4fdcc84dfa4a408ea319fb67dd3e3347
msgid "GPIO的引脚在使用时有什么需要注意的？"
msgstr "What should be noted when using GPIO pins?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:46
#: 11279d7ecd654e11a6fcf2b795e38448
msgid "需要正确配置GPIO结构体，不建议同时使能input与output。"
msgstr ""
"The GPIO structure must be configured correctly. It is not recommended to "
"enable input and output at the same time."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:50
#: 8bdc67b3921e4e618c300febbe03ba57
msgid "SPI一次最多发送多少字节？发送机制是什么？"
msgstr ""
"What is the maximum number of bytes that SPI can send at one time? What is "
"the transmission mechanism?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:51
#: 07e3026d9ff94fc0bdd398bf631148c7
msgid ""
"SPI一次可发送任意长度个字节，只需要保持tx fifo中有持续可用的数据，另外tx fifo"
"的宽度可根据需要设置为8/16/24/32-bit。 发送机制是：使能spi发送功能之后，tx "
"fifo中的数据会按照设定的位宽和bit顺序进入移位寄存器中，然后按照极性和相位的设"
"置在每一个时钟的上升沿/下降沿去改变MISO/MOSI的引脚电平将数据发送出去。 例如"
"CPOL=1，CPHA=1，则SPI时钟空闲时为高电平，数据在时钟的上升沿被送出。"
msgstr ""
"SPI can send any number of bytes at one time, as long as there is "
"continuously available data in the tx fifo. In addition, the width of the tx "
"fifo can be set to 8/16/24/32-bit as needed. The transmission mechanism is: "
"after enabling the SPI transmit function, data in the tx fifo enters the "
"shift register according to the configured bit width and bit order, and "
"then, according to the polarity and phase settings, the MISO/MOSI pin level "
"is changed on each rising/falling edge of the clock to send the data out. "
"For example, when CPOL=1 and CPHA=1, the SPI clock is high when idle, and "
"data is output on the rising edge of the clock."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:57
#: 06a9b3d32ded481e9df5468d3bf77a1d
msgid "模组是否支持播放/录音的功能，支持哪些常用的频率和位宽？"
msgstr ""
"Does the module support playback/recording functions? What common "
"frequencies and bit widths are supported?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:58
#: aef4d485f78c41579591af7643b16338
msgid ""
"模组内置12-bit ADC以及10-bit DAC，可以通过ADC和DAC的基本功能配合推荐的功放/录"
"音电路，完成播放和录音的功能。 仅支持8K常用采样率16-bit位宽播放，因为DAC的时"
"钟仅支持32K 16K 8K 512K四种采样率可选，没有专业的audio PLL ，只有8K是常用的播"
"放采样率，其他采样率不常用。"
msgstr ""
"The module has a built-in 12-bit ADC and 10-bit DAC. Playback and recording "
"functions can be implemented through the basic functions of the ADC and DAC "
"together with the recommended power amplifier/recording circuit. Only 8K "
"common sampling rate and 16-bit bit-width playback are supported. Because "
"the DAC clock only supports four optional sampling rates: 32K, 16K, 8K, and "
"512K, and there is no dedicated audio PLL. Only 8K is a common playback "
"sampling rate; the other sampling rates are not commonly used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:62
#: 62c4594639d64d8a9fe698b95741afd6
msgid "Ai-WB2-12F模组的AT串口可以关闭作为普通UART通讯口么？"
msgstr ""
"Can the AT serial port of the Ai-WB2-12F module be disabled and used as a "
"normal UART communication port?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:63
#: 85965d3a367a456a9554000b349a648f
msgid "可以的，需要做二次开发。"
msgstr "Yes, secondary development is required."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:66
#: 7e80809855e04c07bd660587867b7a22
msgid "WB2系列的开发上NC引脚是做啥用的"
msgstr "What are the NC pins on WB2 series development boards used for?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:67
#: 83e514414df34954b2f53b0cae7af5b1
msgid "NC表示没有引出该引脚，无法使用"
msgstr "NC means that the pin is not routed out and cannot be used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:70
#: 5774e315a8094da2b1b962950e6d40a6
msgid "WB2系列模组带USB接口吗"
msgstr "Do WB2 series modules have a USB interface?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:71
#: 902b3fe3e95c4637badba624161580de
msgid "不带，模组内部的芯片没有USB相关的引脚接口"
msgstr ""
"No. The chip inside the module does not have USB-related pins or interfaces."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:74
#: 43d4ba68b49b4e3cb399addb254f3a07
msgid "请问WB2-12F模组（AT固件）支持硬件流控么？"
msgstr ""
"Does the WB2-12F module with AT firmware support hardware flow control?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:75
#: f0a2d52f79c243a8b8016f46f26f884e
msgid "不支持；"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:78
#: 53441a8f60fe472ab2bcbc3a23440305
msgid "Ai-WB2-12F的ADC是多少位的"
msgstr "How many bits is the ADC of Ai-WB2-12F?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:79
#: 231189a1ba80470298f923fae1660de9
msgid "ADC为8位"
msgstr "The ADC is 8-bit."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:82
#: be9a3d563a27448398d38cb5ceb984ed
msgid "请问Ai-WB2-07S模组是否支持SPI接口AT指令驱动控制？"
msgstr "Does the Ai-WB2-07S module support SPI-interface AT command control?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:83
#: 281e01ab31d04558b466da49e66107ce
msgid "不支持，出厂固件仅支持串口"
msgstr "No. The factory firmware only supports UART."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:86
#: 43a0959a63e94dc68e6595aa98c7f172
msgid "WB2系列模组的EN引脚有没有必要用三极管实现控制？"
msgstr ""
"Is it necessary to use a transistor to control the EN pin of WB2 series "
"modules?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:87
#: b846409498644de89fe2f6ead5c6b3f7
msgid "不需要。"
msgstr "No."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:90
#: 4e918f0836274f0b8ecbbd50de24b7b9
msgid "WB2-32S开发板有几个串口可以使用，为什么好多引脚都是NC"
msgstr ""
"How many UART ports are available on the WB2-32S development board? Why are "
"many pins NC?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:91
#: 7cae0fa2d3f3451c8ebc8ec781c64abf
msgid ""
"开发板有2个串口可以使用，通过软件定义实现，NC引脚表示该引脚为悬空引脚，不可使"
"用"
msgstr ""
"The development board has 2 UART ports available, implemented through "
"software definition. NC pins indicate floating pins and cannot be used."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:94
#: 655cdb783e0e4a589076d69b2d3da5e7
msgid "WB2系列的串口支持硬件流控吗"
msgstr "Do the UART ports of WB2 series support hardware flow control?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:95
#: 7521bbe5eb0746c08fc148ab02550139
msgid "需做开发实现，默认不支持硬件流控"
msgstr ""
"It needs to be implemented through development. Hardware flow control is not "
"supported by default."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:98
#: 3625860dc5bc48359f656b90724970b0
msgid "请问WB2-32S模组没有SDIO接口么？"
msgstr "Does the WB2-32S module not have an SDIO interface?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:99
#: 47f9207f51004192a6b580a0938ad59e
msgid "有的；"
msgstr "Yes, it does."

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:103
#: c57b0ac5036b4fb29819f9a77bab3f3c
msgid "WB2-07S这个RST引脚和EN引脚有什么区别吗"
msgstr "What is the difference between the RST pin and EN pin of WB2-07S?"

#: ../source/docs/software-framework/WiFi/BL/peripherals.rst:104
#: f86b61d64d014fb8a5bd28b4e6557919
msgid ""
"没有区别，只是模块默认通过EN引脚进行复位，如果需要通过RST进行复位需要修改模组"
"内部硬件实现"
msgstr ""
"There is no difference. The module resets through the EN pin by default. If "
"reset through RST is required, the module's internal hardware needs to be "
"modified."
